---
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Roam Outfitters — Design Concepts</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
    <style is:global>
        body {
            background: #0f0e0d;
            color: #e8e4df;
            font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .concepts-page {
            max-width: 960px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 80px 24px 120px;
        }

        .concepts-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 80px;
        }

        .concepts-header .label {
            font-size: 11px;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .concepts-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0 0 16px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .concepts-header p {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #888;
            max-width: 520px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .concepts-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .concept-card {
            display: block;
            background: #1a1917;
            border: 1px solid #2a2825;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .concept-card:hover {
            border-color: #c49a3c;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            background: #1f1e1b;
        }

        .concept-card .number {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #c49a3c;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .concept-card h2 {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0 0 8px;
        }

        .concept-card .tagline {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #c49a3c;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .concept-card p {
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #999;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .concept-card .arrow {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #c49a3c;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .concept-card:hover .arrow {
            transform: translateX(4px);
        }

        .concepts-footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 80px;
            padding-top: 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid #2a2825;
        }

        .concepts-footer a {
            color: #c49a3c;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .concepts-footer a:hover {
            color: #d4aa4c;
        }

        .concepts-footer p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="concepts-page">
        <header class="concepts-header">
            <div class="label">Design Exploration</div>
            <h1>Roam Outfitters</h1>
            <p>Four alternative design interpretations of the same content, images, and brand. Each takes a dramatically different approach to tone, layout, and visual language.</p>
        </header>

        <div class="concepts-grid">
            <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}alt/dirtbag`} class="concept-card">
                <div class="number">Concept I</div>
                <h2>The Dirtbag Chronicle</h2>
                <div class="tagline">If the current site is a whiskey bar, this is the campfire outside it.</div>
                <p>Leans all the way into "A Gentleman's Dirtbag Club." Warm, irreverent, funny — like Brett telling you about his life over beers. Scrapbook-style layout with scattered polaroid photos, torn paper edges, camp aesthetic. The personality is the product.</p>
                <span class="arrow">View concept →</span>
            </a>

            <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}alt/cinematic`} class="concept-card">
                <div class="number">Concept II</div>
                <h2>Cinematic Stillness</h2>
                <div class="tagline">Standing alone on the riverbank at dawn.</div>
                <p>Ultra-minimal, meditative, and contemplative. One image at a time, surrounded by vast whitespace. Poetic micro-copy whispered beneath grand photography. The site becomes an experience you slowly scroll through — selling the feeling of escape.</p>
                <span class="arrow">View concept →</span>
            </a>

            <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}alt/editorial`} class="concept-card">
                <div class="number">Concept III</div>
                <h2>Adventure Editorial</h2>
                <div class="tagline">The long-form profile of the bartender in a beautiful magazine you find there.</div>
                <p>Redesigned as a feature spread in a high-end outdoor magazine. Drop caps, pull quotes, full-bleed photography, and literary narrative. Third-person profile: "Brett Seng has spent two decades learning the language of Montana's rivers..."</p>
                <span class="arrow">View concept →</span>
            </a>

            <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}alt/bold`} class="concept-card">
                <div class="number">Concept IV</div>
                <h2>Bold Territory</h2>
                <div class="tagline">The matte-black Yeti cooler in the back of the truck.</div>
                <p>High-energy, modern, confident. Dark-dominant with massive typography, sharp geometry, and electric teal accents. Positions Roam Outfitters like a premium outdoor brand. Short, punchy copy with swagger: "23 years. Six rivers. One obsession."</p>
                <span class="arrow">View concept →</span>
            </a>
        </div>

        <footer class="concepts-footer">
            <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}`}>← Back to current site</a>
            <p>These are unlisted concepts for internal review only.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
